name: ImNotTheWolf
description: $WOLF is a token created by ImNotTheWolf, a crypto influencer and trader on X (formerly Twitter). It builds a shared fund using fees from PumpFun, commissions from What.Exchange affiliates, and ImNotTheWolf's fund management. Profits from this fund go toward buying back and burning tokens to make them scarcer, plus marketing to grow the project. This setup helps holders by reducing supply and boosting visibility through smart spending.
